OL,3,CRyan Reynolds and Hugh Jackman urge
OL,4,Cfans to be 'heroes' by donating blood
OL,6,FHollywood stars Ryan Reynolds and Hugh
OL,7,FJackman have called on fans to be
OL,8,F"heroes" by donating blood in a new
OL,9,Fvideo appeal.
OL,11,FThe collaboration with NHS Blood and
OL,12,FTransplant comes ahead of the launch
OL,13,Fof their superhero movie Deadpool &
OL,14,FWolverine later this month.
OL,16,F"Our characters have spilt countless
OL,17,Fhot tubs worth of blood in the name of
OL,18,Fentertainment, but don't worry it's
OL,19,Fall fake ` mostly", Vancouver-born
OL,20,FReynolds says in the clip.
