OL,3,CRyan Reynolds and Hugh Jackman urge
OL,4,Cfans to be 'heroes' by donating blood
OL,6,FAustralian actor Jackman adds: "Real
OL,7,Fblood is harder to come by, that's why
OL,8,Fthe NHS needs heroes like you to
OL,9,Fdonate blood."
OL,11,FThe upcoming collaboration film which
OL,12,Fopens in cinemas on July 25, sees
OL,13,FReynolds return to his role as the
OL,14,Ffoul-mouthed anti-hero Deadpool, while
OL,15,FHugh Jackman reprised his role as the
OL,16,Falmost indestructible Wolverine.
