OL,3,CRyan Reynolds and Hugh Jackman urge
OL,4,Cfans to be 'heroes' by donating blood
OL,6,FDirector of donor experience for NHS
OL,7,FBlood and Transplant, Mark Chambers,
OL,8,Fsaid he is delighted the pair are
OL,9,Fhighlighting "the lifesaving power of
OL,10,Fblood donation".
OL,12,F"Deadpool saves the day, but blood
OL,13,Fdonors save lives. We hope film fans
OL,14,Fwill be inspired to become a hero in
OL,15,Ftheir own story by giving blood," said
OL,16,FMr Chambers.
OL,18,FThe NHS urgently needs younger donors
OL,19,Fparticularly from Black heritage
OL,20,Fbackgrounds to help patients who
OL,21,Frequire ethnically matched blood.
