OL,3,CRyan Reynolds and Hugh Jackman urge
OL,4,Cfans to be 'heroes' by donating blood
OL,6,FThe clip will be shown in cinemas with
OL,7,Fthe slogan "be the giving type"
OL,8,Freferencing Reynolds' closing tongue-
OL,9,Fin-cheek question "Will you be a giver
OL,10,Fto a receiver in need?".
OL,12,FThe pair hope their message will urge
OL,13,Fviewers to book a blood donation
OL,14,Fappointment with Jackman adding: "Just
OL,15,Fone hour of your time could save up to
OL,16,Fthree lives."
OL,18,FBlood donation appointments can be
OL,19,Fmade at www.blood.co.uk or on the NHS
OL,20,FGive Blood app.
